citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:00pm on 14-SEP-
21. Upon arrival to the facility, inspector knocked on doors at house and kennel, honked from the driveway, and left a
voicemail at the listed number. No response was received within 30 minutes of initial attempts to contact.
End Section
